quran[54]{c,v,t}:
  41,1,"Haa, Miim"
  41,2,"Ko jipporiinde immorde ka Yurmetee…óo, Hinnotoo…óo On"
  41,3,"Deftere fensitaande Aayeeje mun, janngeteende e …óemngal aarabu, wonannde yim…ďe anndoo…ďe"
  41,4,"wewlinaynde jertina. Kono …ďur…ďe …óuu…óude …ďen e ma…ď…ďe, …óuurnii, …ďen …ďe nanataa"
  41,5,"∆Āe wi'i: \"∆Āer…óe amen no ommbanii ko noddataa men e mun kon, noto hino e noppi amen, heedo kadi hino hakkunde amen e maa. Haray wonu e golle maa ; menen kadi me…óen e golle amen"
  41,6,"Maaku: \"Anndee ko ne…ó…óanke yeruujo mon. Wahayinaama e am, wonnde Rewetee…óo mon on, ko Rewetee…óo gooto. √Ďii…ďee e …óum, insinano…óon Mo\". Bone woodanii sirkoo…ďe …ďen"
  41,7,"…ďe jonnataa …ďen zakka, hara kadi hi…ďe yeddi fii laakara"
  41,8,"Pellet, …ďen gom…óim…ďe …ďe golli mo∆ī∆īi …óin, hino woodani …ďe njo…ďdi ndi ta∆īondirtaa"
  41,9,"Maaku: \"E onon on yedday On tagu…óo leydi ndin nder bal…óe …ói…ói, wa…óanon Mo goree…ďe? Awa ko On woni Jey…óo winndere nden. @Corrected"
  41,10,"O wa…ói pelle e dow mayri, O hebbini barki e mayri, O e…ď…ďi nguureeji mayri …óin e nder bal…óe nayi timmu…óe, wonannde lamndotoo…ďe …ďen. @Corrected"
  41,11,"Refti O fotondiri ka kammu, fewndo ka ngu curkinnoo, O daalidani ngun kanngu e leydi ndin: \"Ardiree …óoftaare, maa karheede\". ∆äi wi'idi: \"Men arii ko men …óoftii …ďe\". @Corrected"
  41,12,"O timminiri …ói kammuuli jee…ói…ói nder bal…óe …ói…ói, O yamiri kala kammu, fiyaaku maggu. Men cu…óiniri kammu aduna ngun, koode e reenir…óum. ∆äum ko e…ď…ďoore Foolu…óo, Anndu…óo On. @Corrected"
  41,13,"Si …ďe …óuurnike, haray wi'u …ďe: \"Men jertinirii on haacaangu, sugu haacaango Aadi'en e Samuuda'en"
  41,14,"nde Nulaa…ďe …ďen ardirannoo…ďe, yeeso ma…ď…ďe e …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe, wonnde: \"Wata on rewu dey, si wanaa Allah\", …ďe wi'i: \"Si Joomi amen haajuno, ko Malaa'ika O jippinaynoo. Awa menen, ko men yeddu…ďe ko nula…óon mun kon"
  41,15,"Aadii'en kan, …ďe mawnintini ka hoore leydi, ko aldaa e goonga, …ďe wi'i: \"Hara ko hommbo …ďuri men doole?\" E …ďee yi'aali, wonnde Allah tagu…óo …ďe On no …ďuri …ďe tii…óude doole? ∆Āe woni e yeddugol Aayeeje Amen …óen"
  41,16,"Men wurti henndu …ďuu…ďundu e ma…ď…ďe e √Īalaa…óe hiitaa…óe, fii no Men mee…óinira …ďe lepte koyeera …óen ka nguurndam aduna. Pellet, ko lepte laakara …óen …ďuri wonnde koyeera, kadi …ďe faaboytaake"
  41,17,"Samuuda'en kan, Men …ďannginanno …ďe; kono …ďe su…ďii bum…óam …óam e dow peewal ngal. Dillere lepte hoynooje …óen nanngiri …ďe, sabu ko …ďe faggitotonoo kon"
  41,18,Men da…óndi gom…óim…ďe …ďe woniina hulnoo…ďe …ďen
  41,19,√Ďalnde non ay…ďe Allah …ďen moo…ďiroytee faade ka Yiite... Hara hi…ďe √Īo∆ī∆īindiree
  41,20,"Haa si …ďe hewtii nge, nann…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, e gii…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, e guri …ďalli ma…ď…ďe …óin seeditoo e dow ma…ď…ďe, kon ko …ďe gollaynoo"
  41,21,"∆Āe wi'ana guri ma…ď…ďe …óen: \"Ko fii honn…óum seeditani…óon e amen?\" ∆äe wi'a: \"Ko Allah wowlin…óo kala huunde On, wowlini men. Ko Kanko tagunoo on gila ka laawol aranol, ko ka Makko kadi ruttete…óon"
  41,22,"On wonaali hi…óon suu…óora, fii wata nan…óe mon, e gii…óe mon, e guri mon seedito e mon. Kono on sikkuno, wonnde Allah anndaa ko …óuu…ói e ko huuwoton"
  41,23,"Ko …óum moo…óon, wonunoo ko sikkuno…óon Joomi mon, …óum halki on. Wa…ótin…óon jeyaa…ďe e pertu…ďe …ďen"
  41,24,"Hay si …ďe mu√Ī√Īike, ko Yiite ngen wonata jaa∆īorde ma…ď…ďe; si …ďe …óa…ď…ďii feleede accitee, …ďe wonaali feletee…ďe accitee"
  41,25,"Men wurtani …ďe wondii…ďe, …ďen cu…óinani …ďe ko woni yeeso ma…ď…ďe, e ko woni …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe. Konngol [lepte] ngol jojji e ma…ď…ďe, wondude e mofte yawtunoo…óe ado ma…ď…ďe, immorde e jinna e yim…ďe. Pellet, …ďe laatino hayru…ďe"
  41,26,"Yeddu…ďe …ďen wi'i: \"Wata on jentito ndee Alqur'aanaare, sonkee e mayre (tuma nde janngetee) belajo'o, on foolay"
  41,27,"Ma Men mee…óiniroy yeddu…ďe …ďen, lepte sa…ótu…óe, Men yo…ďira ko …ďuri bonde e ko …ďe huuwaynoo kon"
  41,28,"Ko …óum woni njo…ďdi ay…ďe Allah …ďen: Ko Yiite ngen. Ko galle luttugol woodani …ďe ton, njo…ďdi kon ko …ďe yeddiraynoo Aayeeje Amen …óen"
  41,29,"Yeddu…ďe …ďen wi'a: \"Joomi amen, hollii men majjinnoo…ďe men …ďen ka jinna e ka yim…ďe, men yaa…ďa …ďe men fuga, haa …ďe wona e …ďur…ďe joltude …ďen"
  41,30,"Pellet, wi'u…ďe …ďen : \"Joomi amen ko Allah\", refti …ďe tabiti; Malaa'ika'en hino jippoo e ma…ď…ďe (wiide): \"Wata on hulu, wata on suno; wewliree Aljanna, on mo wonano…óon fodeede"
  41,31,"Ko menen woni walloo…ďe on …ďen ka nguurndam aduna e ka laakara. Hino woodani on ton, kala ko wonkiiji mon woo…óetee, hino woodani ton, kala ko noddoton"
  41,32,"ko maraari, immorde e Haforoore, Hinnotoo…óo"
  41,33,"Hara ko hommbo …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude konngol, wano on noddu…óo e fii Allah, o golli mo∆ī∆īere, o wi'i: \"Min, ko e juul…ďe …ďen mi jeyaa"
  41,34,"Mo∆ī∆īere nden fotataa e bone on. Du√Īir (golle bon…óe …óen) kon ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude; e jaka yoo, on mo ngayngu woni hakkunde maa e mun, himo wa'ita wa gi…óo sa…ótu…óo giggol"
  41,35,"Kono hawrataa e …óum, si wanaa mu√Ī√Īii…ďe …ďen; hawrataa e …óum, si wanaa jom ge…ďal mawnungal"
  41,36,"Si sowinsinoore arii he…ďude ma immorde e seytaane, moolor Allah. Kanko ko O Nanoowo, Anndu…óo"
  41,37,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko …óin, jemma on e √Īalorama on, e naange ngen e lewru ndun. Wata on sujjan naange ngen wanaa kadi lewru ndun. Sujjanee Allah, tagu…óo …ói On, si wonii ko Kanko rewoton"
  41,38,"Si …ďe townitike, …ďen won…ďe ka Joomi maa kan, hi…ďe subbunhinorana Mo jemma e √Īalorma, hara …ďe haa…ďataa"
  41,39,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko …óin, tawde a yi'ay leydi ndin no yoori. Si wonii Men jippinii ndiyam to…ďo e mayri, ndi dilla ndi fontoo. Awa wuurnitu…óo ndi On, pellet, ko wuurnitoowo maay…ďe …ďen, tawde pellet, ko O hattan…óo haka huunde"
  41,40,"Pellet, oo√Īotoo…ďe …ďen e Aayeeje Amen …óen, …ďe suu…óotaako Men. E ko feroytee…óo on ka Yiite …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude kaa ko aroyoowo on √Ďalnde Darngal hino hoolii? Gollee ko faala…óon, ko pellet, Himo reeni ko golloton kon"
  41,41,"Yeddu…ďe …ďen Alqur'aana tuma nde arunoo e ma…ď…ďe, pellet non, ko nde Deftere teddunde [foolunde]"
  41,42,"meere iwrantaa nde yeeso mayre, wanaa …ďaawo mayre. Ko jipporiinde immorde ka √Ďeenyo, Yettinii…óo On"
  41,43,"A wi'aaka si wanaa ko Nulaa…ďe adinoo…ďe ma …ďen wi'anoo. Pellet, Joomi maa, ko O Jom yaafuyee, e Jom lepte muusu…óe"
  41,44,"Si Men wa…óuno nde janngeteende e haala ajami, …ďe wi'ayno: \"Ko ha…óno Aayeeje mayre …óen fensitee? E nde wonay e haala ajami, [Nulaa…óo] on wona aarabuujo?\" Maaku: \"Kayre wonannde gom…óim…ďe …ďen, ko nde peewal e cellal\". ∆Āe gom…óinaa …ďen kan, noto hino e noppi ma…ď…ďe …óin, kayre ko nde ni…ďe e dow ma…ď…ďe; …ďen hino noddiree e nokku wo…ó…óu…óo"
  41,45,"Gom…óii Men okkii Muusaa Deftere nden, nde luutondira e mayre. Si wanaano Konngol ardinoongol immorde ka Joomi maa, hakkunde ma…ď…ďe √Īaaweteno. Kam…ďe kan, pellet, hi…ďe e sikke sikkitii…óo nde"
  41,46,"Kala gollu…óo ko mo∆ī∆īi, ko fii hoore-makko; kala kadi bonnu…óo, yantay e makko. Joomi maa siforaali wonnde, too√Īoowo jeyaa…ďe …ďen"
  41,47,"Ko ka Makko woni ko ganndal Darngal ruttetee. Dim…óe yaltataa e coom…ói mun, deyel (woo) saawataa,ngel jibintaa si wanaa e ganndal Makko.√Ďalnde O noddiroyta …ďe:\"Ko honto woni kafidaa…ói Am …óin?\", …ďe wi'a:\"Men anndinii Ma, alah e amen seedotoo…óo […óum]"
  41,48,∆Āe majjira e kon ko …ďe rewaynoo ko adii; …ďe yananee wonnde da…óirgal alanaa …ďe
  41,49,"Ne…ó…óanke on haa…ďataa toragol mo∆ī∆īere. Si bone memii mo, ko o ta∆īotoo…óo, yonndinii…óo"
  41,50,"Si Men mee…óinir mo mo∆ī∆īere immorde ka Amen, …ďaawo nde lorra memi mo, ko pellet o wi'ay: \"∆äum …óoo ko min ! Mi fellitaani si Darngal daroto. Si mi ruttaama ka Joomi am, ko pellet, mo∆ī∆īere hino woodani lam ka Makko\". Ma Men humpitu yeddu…ďe …ďen, fii ko …ďe huuwi kon, ko ma Men mee…óinoy …ďe lepte sa…ótu…óe"
  41,51,"Si Men neeminii e ne…ó…óanke on, o …óuurnoo o toowna balaaje makko; si bone non he…ďii mo, o wona jom toraare yaajunde"
  41,52,"Maaku: \"Yeetee lam, si wonii le ko ka Allah nde iwri, refti yeddu…óon nde; haray ko hommbo …ďuri majjude on won…óo e lurral wo…ó…óungal"
  41,53,"Aray Men holla …ďe maandeeji Amen …óin ka tatteeji e ma…ď…ďe tigi, haa …ďanngana …ďe wonnde ko nde goonga. E yonaali wonnde Joomi maa, ko O seedii…óo kala huunde"
  41,54,"Anndee hi…ďe e sikke fii hawroygol e Joomi ma…ď…ďe. Anndee non, ko O hu…ďindii…óo kala huunde"